Contributions:

* FountainMode -- screenwriting major mode
* [https://github.com/rnkn/olivetti Olivetti] -- minor mode to balance window margins
* [https://github.com/rnkn/binder Binder] -- global minor mode to work with multi-file writing projects
* [https://github.com/rnkn/freeze-it Freeze-It] -- make your previous writing read-only
* [https://github.com/rnkn/side-notes Side Notes] -- quick access to a notes file in a side window

Elsewhere: https://bydasein.com


